          "site_id": "waytoagi",
          "published_at": "2026-07-05T15:13:58.934250Z"
        },
        {
          "id": "b6fb13bc6400a1e232fc2f954f8e82103e806cd1",
          "title": "不少开发者用 Codex 产出大量半成品项目，因为缺少版本管理反复重做白白浪费精力。芋头小宝这套零基础GitHub实操方案完美解决了项目杂乱丢失的问题。",
          "url": "https://waytoagi.feishu.cn/wiki/QPe5w5g7UisbEkkow8XcDmOpn8e?fromScene=spaceOverview",
          "source": "社区更新 · 2026-07-05",
          "source_name": "WaytoAGI",
          "site_id": "waytoagi",
          "published_at": "2026-07-05T15:13:58.934250Z"
        },
